# Windows .ico intentionally excluded: electron-builder's app-builder icon-converter
# panics packaging NSIS with any .ico here (Pillow- and png2icons-generated tested,
# both fail identically on Windows CI runners). NSIS falls back to Electron's default
# icon instead. Regenerate at build/icon.ico locally with `node scripts/generate_icons.js`
# if a future electron-builder version fixes this and you want to re-enable it.
build/icon.ico
